# Managing LVM Volumes

## Get information about physical volumes

    sudo pvs
    sudo pvdisplay
    sudo pvs -v --segments
    sudo pvs -v --segments /dev/sda5

## Get information about volume groups

    sudo vgs
    sudo vgdisplay

## Get information about logical volumes

    sudo lvs
    sudo lvdisplay

